text: Mélissa Alvès (born 29 December 1993 in Kourouhttp://www.pennathletics.com/roster.aspx?rp_id=11188 French Guiana) is a French professional squash player. As of October 2018, she was ranked number 139 in the world. ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:French female squash players Category:Penn Quakers women's squash players
